R00005: The directionality of reactions and connected pairs of metabolites were inferred from the map version of the reaction formula: ftp.genome.jp/pub/kegg/ligand/ reaction/reaction_mapformula.lst. We then kept only the metabolites located upstream of the central metabolism. This left us with 1813 metabolites. The second tab in the Excel file contains all KEGG reactions connecting 4156 metabolites before we imposed the condition that they must be located upstream of central metabolism.
